quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  11,54,"Icyo twavuga ni uko zimwe mu mana zacu zaguteje ibyago (kuko ubuza abantu kuzisenga). Aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri njye ntanze Allah ho umuhamya, kandi namwe nimube abahamya ko rwose nitandukanyije n’ibyo mumubangikanya musenga,",""
  11,55,"Bitari We (Allah). Ngaho nimuncurire imigambi mibisha mwese kandi ntimundindirize.”",""
  11,56,"“Mu by’ukuri njye niringiye Allah, Nyagasani wanjye akaba na Nyagasani wanyu. Nta kiremwa na kimwe gifite ubugingo Allah atagenga. Rwose, Nyagasani wanjye ni We ufite inzira igororotse.”",""
  11,57,"“Ubwo nimutera umugongo (ukuri, mumenye ko) njye namaze kubagezaho ubutumwa nahawe, kandi Nyagasani wanjye azabasimbuza abandi bantu, ndetse nta cyo muzamutwara. Mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wanjye ni Umurinzi wa byose.”",""
  11,58,"Ubwo isezerano ryacu (ryo guhana abigometse) ryasohoraga, twarokoye Hudu n’abemeye hamwe na we ku bw'impuhwe ziduturutseho, maze tubakiza ibihano bikomeye.",""
  11,59,"Abo bari (abantu bo) mu bwoko bw’aba Adi. Bahakanye ibimenyetso bya Nyagasani wabo, bigomeka ku ntumwa ze, banakurikira amategeko ya buri mwibone wese winangira (utava ku izima).",""
  11,60,"Kandi bakurikijwe umuvumo muri iyi si ndetse (uzanabakurikirana) no ku munsi w’imperuka. Nta gushidikanya ko mu by’ukuri ubwoko bw’aba Adi bwahakanye Nyagasani wabwo. Barakarimbuka ba Adi, ari bo bantu ba Hudu!",""
  11,61,"N’abantu bo mu bwoko bw’aba Thamudu, twaboherereje umuvandimwe wabo Swalehe, aravuga ati “Yemwe bantu banjye! Nimugaragire Allah! Nta yindi mana mufite ikwiye gusengwa itari We. Ni We wabahanze abakomoye mu gitaka anakibatuzaho. Bityo, nimumusabe imbabazi kandi munamwicuzeho, kuko mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wanjye ari hafi, kandi asubiza ubusabe.”",""
  11,62,"Baravuga bati “Yewe Swalehe! Mbere y’ibyo (uvuze by’uko tugomba kureka imana zacu), twari twiringiye ko uzaba umutware wacu. Ese uratubuza kugaragira ibyo abakurambere bacu basengaga? Mu by’ukuri twe dufite ugushidikanya guteye inkeke ku kuri kw’ibyo uduhamagarira (udutera guhuzagurika.)”",""
